<Title>Wing Midspan Fixed Trailing Edge Lower Removable Panels</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One per wing may be missing.</Para>
<Para>For model 787-9 or 787-10, the two most inboard panels on each wing may not be missing.</Para>
<Para>On the MISC SYSTEM CTRLS (MSC) maintenance page, set the Overspeed Warning switch to GEAR DOWN.</Para>
<Para>Limit speed to 270 KIAS/0.73 Mach. Note: Do not apply Appendix 1, Landing Gear Extended performance penalties.</Para>
<Para>Reduce performance limited weights for each missing panel by:</Para>
